":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"而加呢個秦王咪係第9世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2世篡奪初代,而初代秦王鄭信死前詛咒&ldquo;奪我王位者，九世而亡&rdquo;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:55:57.000Z","msg":"秦王係姓鄭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"初代咪姓鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4d3d8bc639df31b9bbcc945181db90b8f4e763","tid":2218647,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de8269049ab2816d6d5a9d160b9ec2b448b5fd21","tid":2218647,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e446775cb0aad47b452df05fe6d4a4daf38b98ad","tid":2218647,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07ff567e1342cf229e3831c4957f0420f97c78ac","tid":2218647,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"控制半個國家財政"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:05:31.000Z","msg":"泰國啲商賈財閥生意基本上係皇室御准壟斷，睇下當城啲華裔富豪生意背景就知了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:10:52.000Z","msg":"King power<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:20:14.000Z","msg":"成盤生意傳左畀個仔"},{"pid":"b911bb137159c35f69cc775c9a82f8575cb270cd","tid":2218647,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e39b051cdb799b9698ff626e77dc1948aef17d2b","tid":2218647,"uid":244240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:40:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9299448103c796efe53ddd31d996565502edfde3","tid":2218647,"uid":102331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:51:04.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 泰國手足面對緊自己政府暴政都仍然無忘記香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[奶茶聯盟]泰國盟友準備十一去中國大使館賀佢老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2219130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2219130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"498bc8f9d99629b55bdfa3803356cd62ebfd79f3","tid":2218647,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7cd150ae1b9e844e7073d2d73789ca5fe1b65f","tid":2218647,"uid":24615,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"泰國放權落黎，下場就係英國皇室/西班牙皇室；若然堅持鎮壓，過多排下場就係法國/俄羅斯皇室。"},{"pid":"f9e57763782afe79f6a83b3e44c6f5e7be763cb6","tid":2218647,"uid":160502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd7cd150ae1b9e844e7073d2d73789ca5fe1b65f","tid":2218647,"uid":24615,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"泰國放權落黎，下場就係英國皇室/西班牙皇室；若然堅持鎮壓，過多排下場就係法國/俄羅斯皇室。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:14:23.000Z","msg":"你諗吓秦國個傻仔咩性格<br />\n一定係用鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}